To build the documentation, you will need sphinx and several extensions.
Install with pip by running
```
$ pip install --user sphinx myst-parser sphinx-rtd-theme
```
or with conda
```
$ conda install sphinx myst-parser sphinx-rtd-theme
```

To build the documentation in html format, run
```
$ make html
```
in this directory. Several other formats are available, run `$ make` to see a
list.
